    "content": "Create assets/scss/\nFiles that begin with _ are not meant to be imported into the SASS compiler. They are meant to be used by other scss files.\nmain.scss file Import other _ files that are in assets/scss:\n@import \"grid\"; @import \"demo\";Import SCSS or SASS Add to /layouts/partials/head.html\n\u003ctitle\u003e{{ .Title }}\u003c/title\u003e {{ $css := resources.Get \"scss/main.scss\" }} {{ $css = $css | toCSS }} \u003clink rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"{{ $css.RelPermalink}}\"\u003e",
    "description": "",
