    "content": "Pandoc Used for converting file formats\nhttps://ins3cure.com/pandoc-on-rhel-8/\nGo to https://github.com/jgm/pandoc/releases/latest, download the latest tarball (currently pandoc-2.17.0.1-linux-64.tar.gz) and run:\nsudo tar xvzf pandoc-2.17.0.1-linux-64.tar.gz --strip-components 1 -C /usr/local/install TeX to be able to generate PDF output:\nsudo yum -y install texliveBasic useage pandoc inputfile -f inputfiletype -t outputfiletype -o outputfileConvert full folder for f in *; do pandoc \"$f\" -s -o \"../bloghtml/${f%}.html\"; done",
